This is a 29 minute workout called '30 Min FULL BODY DUMBBELL WORKOUT To Burn Fat | Best Dumbbell Exercises for Ages 50+' from the channel fabulous50s.
The workout falls under Strength/Weight workout.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
You'll need Weights for this workout.
The workout has a The Foundation Builder and The Disciplined Grind vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.

Join me as we warm up, set our intention, and push ourselves to be proud of what our bodies can achieve. From single-hand rows to sumo squats, shoulder presses to tricep extensions, every move is crafted to challenge you and adapt to your fitness level. Remember, the goal is to feel strong and confident!
